'''藍玫瑰'''包含了轉基因的玫瑰[[品種|品種]]和染色後的玫瑰。

自然界中并不存在蓝色的玫瑰。第一種轉基因合成的藍玫瑰品種，由日本[[三得利|三得利]]公司在2004年首次培育成功<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/st/2006-06/05/content_4646013.htm |title=5000多年基因難題破解 日本造出藍色玫瑰 |access-date=2016-05-18 |archive-date=2017-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170326102334/http://news.xinhuanet.com/st/2006-06/05/content_4646013.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該品種由於含有[[翠雀花素|翠雀花素]]（一種[[花青素|花青素]]）而呈色；<ref name=physorg>{{cite web|work=Phys.Org website|date=2005-04-04|url=http://www.physorg.com/news3581.html|title=Plant gene replacement results in the world's only blue rose|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205020758/http://www.physorg.com/news3581.html|archivedate=2012-02-05|access-date=2019-09-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Danielle Demetriou|date=2008-10-31|work=The Daily Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/japan/3329213/Worlds-first-blue-roses-after-20-years-of-research.html|title=World's first blue roses after 20 years of research|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203141250/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/japan/3329213/Worlds-first-blue-roses-after-20-years-of-research.html|archivedate=2017-12-03|accessdate=2019-09-13}}</ref>雖然取名「藍玫瑰」，它真正的花色介於薰衣草色和[[藕合色|藕合色]]之間。<ref>{{cite web|author=Nosowitz, Dan|date=2011-09-15|url=http://www.popsci.com/science/article/2011-09/suntory-creates-mythical-blue-or-um-lavender-ish-rose|title=Suntory Creates Mythical Blue (Or, Um, Lavender-ish) Rose|work=Popular Science|accessdate=2012-08-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111224182130/http://www.popsci.com/science/article/2011-09/suntory-creates-mythical-blue-or-um-lavender-ish-rose|archivedate=2011-12-24}}</ref>
天津大学和中科院的研究人员在2018年也用[[白玫瑰|白玫瑰]]通过[[转基因|转基因]]技术培育出了藍玫瑰<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nanjaraj Urs |first1=Ankanahalli N. |last2=Hu |first2=Yiling |last3=Li |first3=Pengwei |last4=Yuchi |first4=Zhiguang |last5=Chen |first5=Yihua |last6=Zhang |first6=Yan |title=Cloning and Expression of a Nonribosomal Peptide Synthetase to Generate Blue Rose |journal=ACS Synthetic Biology |date=2018-09-18 |doi=10.1021/acssynbio.8b00187}}</ref>。

藍色妖姬等品種不是真正的藍玫瑰，而是用白玫瑰或白月季染色成的。

在一些文化中，蓝玫瑰传统上与"蓝色"皇室血液联系在一起，因此蓝玫瑰代表王权和辉煌。 由于蓝玫瑰实质上的缺失，它们也象征神秘和渴望实现不可能的事物。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gardenguides.com/70125-blue-roses.html|title=About Blue Roses|work=GardenGuides|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100713083157/http://www.gardenguides.com/70125-blue-roses.html|archivedate=2010-07-13|accessdate=2018-10-26}}</ref>

